{"parse":{"title":"Raw Rainbow Fin Albacore","pageid":38427,"wikitext":{"*":"<onlyinclude>{{{{{tpl|tooltip}}}\n|mode={{{mode|}}}\n|arg={{{arg|}}}\n|icon=INV_Misc_Fish_25\n|name=Raw Rainbow Fin Albacore\n|quality=common\n|level=5\n|stack=20\n|effect=<u>Use</u>: Restores 61 health over 18 sec. Must remain seated while eating.\n|charges=1\n|sell={{cost|||2}}\n|ilvl=15\n}}</onlyinclude>\nA '''Raw Rainbow Fin Albacore''' is fun to try to catch since it's a fighter and shimmers in the sun when it leaps out of the water.\n\n== Source ==\nThis fish can be caught by [[fishing]] in the waters of [[Ashenvale]], [[Bloodmyst Isle]], [[Darkshore]], [[Durotar]], [[Hillsbrad Foothills]], [[Silverpine Forest]], [[The Barrens]], [[Westfall]], and the [[Wetlands]].\n\n== Raw Rainbow Fin Albacore as an Ingredient ==\n\n=== Cooking ===\n*[[Rainbow Fin Albacore]]\n\n==External links==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{elinks-item|6361}}\n{{Elink|link=http://www.elsanglin.com/fish/raw_rainbow_fin_albacore.html |site=El's Extreme Anglin' |icon=elsanglin}}\n\n[[Category:World of Warcraft common fished items]]\n[[Category:World of Warcraft food items]]\n[[Category:World of Warcraft cooking ingredient items]]\n[[Category:Fish]]"}}}